 <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I don't know much about how the EZBoard donations work.<br>
<br>
Are there different donation options to EZboard? Is it possible that people could have donated to EZboard but not have had the money go to a specific board? I'm not sure how the donation system works. I donated before but still got pop up adds on other EZboards (namely the Tunare general one which I'm loath to go to very often).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
There are basically 2 types of donations.<br>
1. Donating to a specific board. You click on the chest of a board and donate x amount of dollars which the boardadmin then can use to buy things like gold status.<br>
2. &quot;Donating to ezboard&quot;. This is simply like buying an account at EZBoard and is a fixed price. With this you can visit all boards without pop-ups (even if there are pop-ups, YOU won't get to see them). Also any board you visit does not count towards that boards &quot;pagehits&quot; on which it's gold status fee and such is determined. So you donate indirectly to your favourite boards with a payed account. Theoretically if all visistors to a board have ezsuporter status the board's gold status would be free <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  <p>Arch Convoker Rhand Drago'Magica<br>
